FIND-065 (major, REQ-EDIT-035, PROP-EDIT-024a): RESOLVED
  File: promptnotes/src/lib/editor/EditorPanel.svelte
  Lines changed: 60-64 (pendingNewNoteSource state), 201-225 ($effect for deferred dispatch),
                 318-325 (handleNewNoteRequest sets pendingNewNoteSource)
  Fix: Added `pendingNewNoteSource = $state<'explicit-button' | 'ctrl-N' | null>(null)`.
       In the editing+dirty branch of handleNewNoteRequest, sets pendingNewNoteSource = source
       then dispatches TriggerBlurSave. A new $effect watches viewState transitions:
       when pendingNewNoteSource !== null AND (status==='editing' && !isDirty) OR status==='idle',
       it dispatches RequestNewNote and clears the flag. On save-failed, clears the flag
       so the user must resolve via the banner.

