3. block-element.dom.vitest.ts > REQ-EDIT-006: Enter at end of non-empty block dispatches InsertBlock
   Reason: Test expects InsertBlockAfter from querySelector('[data-testid="block-element"]').
   Without ghost, first block is block-1 (index=0, content='hello'). The $effect focuses
